antichess
Class ChessMove

java.lang.Object
  antichess.Move
      antichess.ChessMove

public class ChessMove
extends Move

A ChessMove represents a move in a Chess game. ChessMoves are immutable.

Specification Fields
  • row : int // The row the piece is moving to
  • column : int // The column the piece is moving to
  • capturedPiece : Piece // The piece that is captured by this Move. May be null.
